text: Chiyoko, how about taking a break soon?

You've been particularly enthusiastic lately. ...especially
with the 283 Live coming up soon. It's only natural.
And I can't afford to hold back and let everyone down!

Above all else, having more options than just Houkura
is what makes it exciting for the fans who come to see us.
I have to work hard to keep them watching me!

...It's because of that attitude, Chiyoko, that I'm sure
everyone won't be able to take their eyes off you.
